Title: Includes digital health care service platforms in the definition of temporary health care services agency
Summary: Includes digital health care service platforms in the definition of temporary health care services agency; includes the connection of health care personnel to services at a health care entity in the term assign.
LawCode: Amd ยง2999-ii, Pub Health L
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law, in relation to including digital health care service platforms in the definition of temporary health care services agency
